Please follow @yorkshiresquarebrewery for more info!

 ----------------------------------------------------------

#Repost with @Repostlyapp @yorkshiresquarebrewery Black Is Beautiful! We are excited to announce the release of Black Is Beautiful, an imperial stout brewed in support of the efforts of our friends at @weatheredsoulsbrewing in San Antonio.
.
Our version of this beer is decidedly English, utilizing British malts and an English yeast strain making this beer rich and complex with notes of dark chocolate, coffee, dark fruit, and hints of tobacco. At 7.2% ABV, it‚Äôs dangerously drinkable and available NOW for you to enjoy on our socially distant patio or to-go in a crowler.
.
This beer has been brewed in solidarity with over 1,000 breweries around the world, in an attempt to bring awareness to the injustices that many people of color face daily. This mission is also an affirmation that the craft brewing community is a place of inclusion for people of all colors and walks of life. For our part, we‚Äôll be donating a portion of the proceeds to NMAC (National Minority AIDS Council), an organization that‚Äôs determined to normalize discussion of race within the HIV movement, bend the curve of new HIV diagnoses, and retain people of color living with HIV in care.
.
Pick up a crowler today, or enjoy a glass on our patio and join a movement of over 1,000 breweries celebrating black lives. Black Is Beautiful! 

